node.text:
"les détails, tout est dans les détails” As the French always says, the details, is all in the details.

This incredible kitchen was tailor-made to our client's specifications, down to the smallest detail. L'Atelier Paris designs and builds kitchens that go beyond color, material, and finish selection, giving clients the ability to specify the measurements of their choices down to a fraction of an inch.

Dreams are made at home!

@l_atelier_paris, the world's greatest kitchens.
